{"tid":2167961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"新巴城巴正式變中資了","createTime":"2020-08-21T12:19:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T16:55:30.000Z","uid":8318,"like":10,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"1f3a61ab6072ee541115592814f8fc48409a0950","tid":2167961,"uid":8318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:19:36.000Z","msg":"新創建集團宣佈已出售旗下新創建交通服務有限公司 (包括新巴、城巴) 的全數股權予新投資者，作價32億港元，當中「善水資本」為主要股東 (90.8%)，「漢思能源」(上市編號: 0554) 為投資夥伴 (8.6%) ，Ascendal Group 為營運夥伴。新股東承諾現有管理架構及員工福利等會維持不變。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2020/0821/2020082101043_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww1.hkexnews.hk%2Flistedco%2Flistconews%2Fsehk%2F2020%2F0821%2F2020082101043_c.pdf&d=fUB9jTkReJc3fMEQQRliu7TKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=435ba38b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www1.hkexnews.hk/listedco/listconews/sehk/2020/0821/2020082101043_c.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"9132e86422ab54ecfa99e1b0cc8bcb337bbb5188","tid":2167961,"uid":8318,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:21:45.000Z","msg":"大陸巴士炸爆港島不是夢"},{"pid":"d02ca8718fa3dfc1bb3c1faa5ab9dfd3f2e15225","tid":2167961,"uid":155674,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"唔係中資喎<br />\n個主席係法國人黎"},{"pid":"7e63a1f2aa037ebebaf716cf3633c6c45b0cb6d9","tid":2167961,"uid":164435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:37:59.000Z","msg":"國際投資財團收購新巴及城巴<br />\n<br />\n由 Templewater Bravo Holdings Limited (「Templewater Bravo」) 牽頭的國際財團，聯同營運夥伴 Ascendal Group Limited (「Ascendal」) 和投資夥伴漢思能源有限公司 (「漢思能源」)，從新創建集團有限公司 (「新創建」) 購入新世界第一巴士服務有限公司 (「新巴」) 及城巴有限公司 (「城巴」) 的全部權益，總作價為 32 億港元。<br />\n\r<br />\n新巴及城巴共有逾 5,000 名員工，營運約 200 條路線及擁有一支超過 1,700 架巴士的車隊，每日服務約100 萬人次。他們致力為香港提供最好的巴士服務。<br />\n\r<br />\nTemplewater Bravo 是善水資本旗下Templewater I, G.P. 管理及控制的投資公司。善水資本是一間私募股權投資公司， 由 Investec Bank plc (天達銀行) 與張堃先生合作成立。Templewater Bravo 將持有新巴及城巴超過 90%權益。<br />\n\r<br />\n總部設在英國的 Ascendal 是公共交通服務營運專家。作為今次交易的營運夥伴，他們會致力將業界尖端技術與知識引入香港。<br />\n<br />\n而漢思能源則為一間香港上市公司，專注能源產品貿易、倉儲業務以及零售（加油站）業務，是 Templewater Bravo 和 Ascendal 是次交易的投資夥伴。"},{"pid":"8bdaa8e78fb5732f5d80eac2c91fd0b3ab53030e","tid":2167961,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf493a4a60209154ab554a8a6e4d03a1cd8d10d2","tid":2167961,"uid":309044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:45:01.000Z","msg":"有咩分別, 新創建老細係邊個知唔知"},{"pid":"779cb1c23095c79a513f03eb402a48504e5d9313","tid":2167961,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8bdaa8e78fb5732f5d80eac2c91fd0b3ab53030e","tid":2167961,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:40:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:46:26.000Z","msg":"中資？"},{"pid":"226e672b6b1de9ba22b1c16e29729b856e143a57","tid":2167961,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:47:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3049a0cc8b449c394bfc9fe9b95594b9bb7a13cf","tid":2167961,"uid":202340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:49:45.000Z","msg":"咁咪好囉 呢啲業務根本冇錢賺"},{"pid":"167047cdf7275dbcb3b40d6233b5b781cc2948e0","tid":2167961,"uid":51790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d02ca8718fa3dfc1bb3c1faa5ab9dfd3f2e15225","tid":2167961,"uid":155674,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:27:03.000Z","msg":"唔係中資喎<br />\n個主席係法國人黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T12:49:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr